  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD COMMUNITY</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Follow <strong>Samuel </strong>, <strong>Sarah</strong>, and <strong>Clunky</strong>, on a perilous journey through <i>Relic Odyssey: Ruins of Xantao</i>. Brace yourself as you confront disgusting beasts, ruthless smugglers, and the enigmatic \"Collector\" - a mad man who will stop at nothing to obtain the power hidden within the ruins of Xantao.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/264947fa7ee24afca23b23b9fa755001.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/caceb4635ab570432ce8d881f4f7e59e.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/caceb4635ab570432ce8d881f4f7e59e.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/caceb4635ab570432ce8d881f4f7e59e.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fight off</strong> creatures using an array of weapons and gadgets. Experience different types of enemies and fighting styles as you make your way through research centres, lairs, and ruins!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/6701e4cebfc3030087e79936f9b24738.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/800709941b5c20ae20fdeceb48b16726.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/800709941b5c20ae20fdeceb48b16726.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/800709941b5c20ae20fdeceb48b16726.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scan for enemies and resources using your <strong>AVARITE POWERED GLOVES</strong>! Have fun pushing and pulling enemies through lairs and ruins. Use this same ability to manipulate your environment!<br><br>Collect resources for <strong>CRAFTING</strong> new weapons and upgrades! Collect rare resources throughout the lairs and ruins then use them to craft technology like mobile medical bays and upgrades for the drilling rig.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/32c549afbc5e981b3780b61a3c27dc11.poster.avif?t=1737993492\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/32c549afbc5e981b3780b61a3c27dc11.webm?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2297960/extras/32c549afbc5e981b3780b61a3c27dc11.mp4?t=1737993492\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Drill down into the enigmatic depths of the planet Valtar, on a quest to unearth the long-lost city of Xantao. With our <strong>PROCEDURALLY GENERATED LEVELS</strong>, each descent is a new challenge, presenting new environments, enemies, and treasures.",
